   - gui/app_detail.go: AgentStatusInfo, AgentDetailInfo, GetAgentDetail, GetAgentStatuses, GetLocks → 존재 확인
   - gui/cmd/claudestra/main.go: main(), printUsage(), 헬퍼만 → 100줄 이내
   - gui/cmd/claudestra/cmd_team.go: cmdStatus, cmdTeam, cmdTeamSet
   - gui/cmd/claudestra/cmd_session.go: cmdSession, cmdIssues, cmdLeadSession
   - gui/cmd/claudestra/cmd_agent.go: cmdIdea, cmdOutput, cmdAssign 등
   - gui/cmd/claudestra/cmd_config.go: cmdContract, cmdHook, describeToolCall

3. 중복 코드 확인:
